==German==
===Etymology===
Ironic feminine form of "Bulle", a derogative word for a male cop. Obviously because of the homophone "Bulette".
===Noun===
'''Bullette''' ''f''
# (derogative) a female [[cop]]
# (slang) a [[Berlin]] citizen

